Message.Jp: 【週期要請】ミスリウ森林（リンウッド）：治安維持討伐

Message.En:
Lately, the forest has become more dangerous. 
I want to gradually reduce the number of monsters. 
Could you defeat about <LQVA> <LQEM>? 
It's a long-term goal, so there's no rush.
